{"tid":684080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有仙氣）日版《那些年》重現原裝經典","createTime":"2018-05-30T08:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T00:45:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":43,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":103,"replies":[{"pid":"2295eae91e7c57123931b72733aba3daad21054d","tid":684080,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180530/bkn-20180530111115806-0530_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180530%2Fbkn-20180530111115806-0530_00862_001.html&d=MFFHEQWs%2FHKsaOFf84186dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5c254092\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180530/bkn-20180530111115806-0530_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180530/photo/bkn-20180530111115806-0530_00862_001_10p.jpg?20180530124842\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180530%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180530111115806-0530_00862_001_10p.jpg%3F20180530124842&h=65a4ce30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻拍自台灣賣座電影《那些年，我們一起追的女孩》的同名日本電影，由日本當紅女團乃木坂46主將齋藤飛鳥飾演日版沈佳宜，男主角柯景騰由上位男星山田裕貴擔綱。電影將於10月在日本開畫，電影公司搶先於今天公開首支預告片和宣傳海報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/01/16/1217237-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F1217237-XXL.jpg&h=5a6302af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日版《那些年》以2000年代日本為故事背景，並特意走訪台灣取景。預告可見日版重現了不少台版的經典場面，除一眾演員排排坐在海邊的指定動作，還有男主角上堂瞌眼瞓遭女主角用筆篤背脊一幕，以及兩人在台灣約會放天燈的場面等。另一個注目點是他們在戲中的校服設計亦跟足台版，齋藤飛鳥獲不少網友大讚仙氣十足！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.recordchina.co.jp/thumbs/m720/201710/20171027-044114018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.recordchina.co.jp%2Fthumbs%2Fm720%2F201710%2F20171027-044114018.jpg&h=5406cab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1990000/1990740/20180115_year_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1990000%2F1990740%2F20180115_year_01_1024.jpg&h=8f9ec1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN180530-14548-CO9-M&amp;d=1527655247\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DOEN180530-14548-CO9-M%26d%3D1527655247&d=MFFHEQWs%2FHKsaOFf84186dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4396d3b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=OEN180530-14548-CO9-M&amp;d=1527655247</a>"},{"pid":"e3389756224f946b0d3f1babea1e7b442cfa0762","tid":684080,"uid":20317,"like":47,"dislike":91,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"唔夠台版靚"},{"pid":"c59c066df0fe34608dbc34151005aff5df283ba5","tid":684080,"uid":38757,"like":42,"dislike":61,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"唔夠台版黎喎...."},{"pid":"c6888ca91e902aee4e752b76b00d6cfed1d763df","tid":684080,"uid":102096,"like":29,"dislike":68,"score":-39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:44:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1408aca0649758a85073225f5eaee9c179401e1","tid":684080,"uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":30,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://resource.mingweekly.com/userfiles/sm/sm640480_images_A1/12512/2017102566117649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource.mingweekly.com%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm640480_images_A1%2F12512%2F2017102566117649.jpg&h=6de072fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a018ead8667f92a26a0a253ba4d56833e535308e","tid":684080,"uid":60545,"like":78,"dislike":7,"score":71,"quote":{"pid":"c6888ca91e902aee4e752b76b00d6cfed1d763df","tid":684080,"uid":102096,"like":29,"dislike":68,"score":-39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T08:4